decks.notes: The main goal of this deck is to quickly and efficiently bring out aggressive creatures, using Alesha's ability to bring back creatures with power 2 or less from the graveyard. The deck focuses on early aggression and board control, using efficient removal spells and creatures with strong abilities to put pressure on the opponent. By utilizing a mix of creatures with abilities like first strike, protection, and removal, the deck aims to overwhelm the opponent and maintain a strong board presence throughout the game. The deck also includes a mix of lands and spells to support the aggressive strategy, ensuring that the deck can consistently bring out threats and disrupt the opponent's game plan.
